
make run01 directory
take BART.cfg and config_transit.cfg files from Examples directory
edit them with correct information and put them in run01 directory
(currently BART.py cannot distinguish two config file with the same extension, so rename config_transit.cfg to config_transit.txt)
cd to run01 directory
run BART with ../BART.py

to execute just the Initial part in BART.py put return
after:

  # Make transit configuration file:
  mc.makecfg(cfile, date_dir, atmfile)

  return

